title: Extended Timeline v0.11.1 - Europa Universalis IV mod
description:
Up to date for EUIV version 1.8 and all DLC. 

The Extended Timeline starts in the year 51 and continues all the way to the present day. You can play with the ancient Roman Empire, any modern world nation or anything in between. 

Main features: 
- Playable timeline extended to 51-9999. 
- Over 500 new countries, each with historical territories and rulers at any given date. 
- Added over 100 new provinces removing all wastelands. 
- Dozens of new religions, most of which have unique mechanics and decisions. 
- New cultures, technologies, units and buildings. 
- Over 100 new events including the fall of Rome, the birth of Islam and the great schism. 
- About 100 new decisions
